name: Boxer Black and White Dog Silhouette
description:
Looking for a way to show others how much you love your furry friend? These hand painted dog silhouettes are great addition to your home or to give as a special gift. 

This silhouette comes on a 11x14 flat canvas, painted with black acrylic paint. Each canvas is packed safely in bubble wrapped and shipped out in three business days to your home. Add a frame and you are ready to go!

If you do not see your dog or would like a special order, please contact me directly. I can pretty much do any color combination you like (2 colors will cost $5.00 more) and any dog you want. If I don't have the dog, I can take a picture of your dog and make a silhouette out of it.

Feel free to email me for any questions you may have! Thanks for stopping by and looking at my prints.

name: Orange Sherbert Doggie Tutu
description:
Doggies need Tutu's too! 

How adorable will your pet be for your next party or event. Dress her up in an adorable MR handmade tutu and I promise she will be the life of the party. Each tutu is special ordered to fit your dog perfectly. Made with high quality tulle colors of your choice, a no-roll elastic band, and lined with satin ribbon to not irratate your dogs belly.


Small Dog Tutu's are $20.00 (under 12 inch waist)
Large Dog Tutu's are $25.00 (over 12 inch waist)
